    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are explicitly acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 5. The CFD model correctly identifies the worst-case hemolysis operating point, NIH predictions are within ±25% of experimental values across all five operating points, and the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied relative to the predicate device. The package is submitted under the Minimal profile; the digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow and will be applied prior to regulatory submission.",
